OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and settled start to the
OL,6,Fday with hazy sunshine. A few showers
OL,7,Fdeveloping by the afternoon but most
OL,8,Fplaces remaining dry with sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Temperatures down compared to
OL,10,Fprevious days but still warm for the
OL,11,Ftime of year.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy periods to start the
OL,14,Fnight as showers fade. Dry and mild
OL,15,Flater on with skies clearing, and the
OL,16,Fwind easing to a light breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
