OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA bright and sunny start but
OL,6,Fclouding over by late morning. A few
OL,7,Fdrops of rain affecting parts during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon but remaining warm and
OL,9,Fdry for most until evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,12,Fgrey and likely wet start to Tuesday
OL,13,Fwith showers to follow. A settled
OL,14,Fstart to Wednesday but turning wet and
OL,15,Fwindy with heavy showers on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
